title: The Dorling Kindersley Visual Encyclopedia (DK Ebook).pdf
description:
The Dorling Kindersley Visual Encyclopedia
Dorling Kindersley | 1995 | ISBN 1564589854 | English | 462 pages | PDF | 109 MB

From science and technology to plants and animals to flags of the world and sports records and historical events, this lavishly illustrated compendium provides information on 50,000 essential facts. Detailed charts, lists, diagrams, maps, and more than 15,000 full-color photos and illustrations highlight thousands of facts
